TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DAY_DATE as DAY_DATE,CY_YEAR_YYYY AS CY_YEAR_YYYY,CY_MONTH_NUM AS CY_MONTH_NUM,(cy_year_yyyy-1) as LAST_YEAR, case when cy_month_num = '1' then to_number(cy_year_yyyy-1) else to_number(cy_year_yyyy) end as PREV_YYYY, case when cy_month_num = '1' then 12 else to_number(cy_month_num-1) end AS PREV_MONTH_NUM FROM SLBA.DAY_DIMENSION WHERE DAY_DATE=TRUNC(SYSDATE)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT distinct SAP_PROCESS_TABLE.TS_DIV_CDE FROM SAP_PROCESS_TABLE WHERE SAP_PROCESS_TABLE.DIVISION_GROUP!='--'
